<!--     EVENT CALENDAR HEADER DEFINITION     -->
{| style="color: black; background-color: #ddddff;" width="100%;"
| <span style="font-size:175%">Event Calendar</span> 
|}

Please see the [[App.Net_Wiki:Current_events|Current Events page]] for more detail.
==== Weekly events ====
{|
|Monday
|[[MondayNightDanceParty]] - request your favourite music.<br>
|-
|Tuesday
|[[TuesdayChallenge]] - create themed art.<br>
|-
|Wednesday
|[[WednesdayChallenge]] - write a themed 1-post story.<br>
|-
|Friday
|[[GameFriday]] - get your game face on!<br>
|-
|Friday too!
|[[WorkChat]] - get or give tips that help you work smarter.<br>
|-
|Sunday
|[[QuoteSunday]] - post a quote that sums up what you're thinking.<br>
|}

==== Monthly events ====
* Every 15th day of the month - [[BookClub]] - read and discuss a book together.
* Every second Monday of the month - [[ThemeMonday]] (starts on Sunday around noon UTC) - change your avatar to a theme for a day or more.

==== Irregular events ====
* [[Discover_ADN|Discover ADN]] - short podcasts interviewing interesting ADN users. (Released around every 3 days.)
* The [[Firesides|Firesid.es]] community-run chats with ADN users.
|}

